your_project/
│
├── app/                        # Application logic
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── models/                 # Data structures (e.g. ORM or Pydantic models)
│   ├── services/               # Business logic
│   ├── api/ or views/          # Input/output layer (e.g. Flask views, FastAPI routers)
│   ├── schemas/                # Request/response data validation (e.g. Pydantic)
│   └── utils/                  # Helper functions/utilities
│
├── tests/                     # Unit and integration tests
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── ...
│
├── configs/                   # Configuration files (JSON/YAML/TOML/etc.)
│
├── scripts/                   # One-off scripts (migrations, data import/export)
│
├── .env                       # Environment variables
├── .gitignore
├── requirements.txt           # Dependencies
├── pyproject.toml             # Optional: Modern dependency/config (instead of setup.py)
├── Dockerfile                 # If containerized
├── README.md
└── main.py                    # Entry point of the app
